  .yir-columns
    .yir-column.yir-column-left
      .yir-column-title
        STAFF SPOTLIGHT
      .yir-column-content
        .yir-title JIM FERGUESON
        .pull-right= image_tag 'newsletter/jim-fergueson.png', style: 'width: 200px;margin-left: 20px;'
        Our editor, Jim Fergueson, had his third film premiere at this year's
        Short Film Corner at the Cannes Film Festival. Written and produced over
        two years, his film "Overachiever" touches on the harsh realities that
        recent graduates face. It follows one man's journey of realizing that we
        are in a world that doesn't give handouts and "values unreachable
        experience often without offering second chances."
        = link_to 'http://emag.imaginenews.com/755/01-04-2016#page/8' do
          Read more in this article from Imagine Magazine.
    .yir-column.yir-column-center
    .yir-column.yir-column-right
      .yir-column-title.yir-column-title-right
        IN THE NEWS
      .yir-column-content
        Roll out the red carpet! Conductor Productions and media partner Mercury
        Media were nominated for 3 Moxie Awards at the 2016 ERA convention in
        Las Vegas. Quite the honor. The team was nominated in the category Best
        Short Form Variety for Mobile Help and Best Short Form of the Year,
        Brand Response for Stride Rite Snoot. We were happy to take home the
        award for Best Health Show of the Year for Quell Wearable Pain Relief.
        .center{ style: 'margin-top: 10px;' }
          = image_tag 'newsletter/moxie-awards.png', style: 'margin-right: 20px;max-width: 100%'

